1:57:52+09:00 [INFO] PID-11977 TID-ovytbrfzo #processor_died @threads.delete(processor.object_id)\n2016-02-04T11:57:52+09:00 [INFO] PID-11977 TID-ovytbrfzo #processor_died @busy.delete(processor)\n2016-02-04T11:57:52+09:00 [INFO] PID-11977 TID-ovytbrfzo #processor_died shutdown\n2016-02-04T11:57:52+09:00 [INFO] PID-11977 TID-ovytbrfzo #shutdown requeue\n2016-02-04T11:57:52+09:00 [INFO] PID-11977 TID-ovytbrfzo #shutdown finished.signal\n2016-02-04T11:57:52+09:00 [INFO] PID-11977 TID-ovytbrioc #stop condvar.wait\n```\n\nWhen a sidekiq worker shutdowns properly, the log was like\n\n```\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g Terminating 1 quiet workers\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlijq4 #stop condvar.wait\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #stop clean_up_for_graceful_shutdown\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #clean_up_for_graceful_shutdown shutdown\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #shutdown requeue\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #shutdown finished.signal\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #processor_died @in_progress.delete(processor.object_id)\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #processor_died @threads.delete(processor.object_id)\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #processor_died @busy.delete(processor)\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #processor_died shutdown\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #shutdown requeue\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlih1g #shutdown finished.signal\n2016-02-04T12:41:41+09:00 [INFO] PID-29775 TID-ormtlijq4 #stop manager.terminate\n```\n\nSo, there are racy situations that [`@finish.signal`](https://github.com/sonots/sidekiq/commit/5bf39debdae1085396074f78f6f4108881517998#diff-c03646bdb41f0ad59a0ae8796f8fc080R241) are called before [`@condvar.wait`](https://github.com/sonots/sidekiq/commit/5bf39debdae1085396074f78f6f4108881517998#diff-8b1e439c6fe15c4aaf01ec94660173f8R62)\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/2813/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sidekiq/sidekiq/issues/2813/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"}]